title: Club Chats
body: Hi gang, pretty new to this alpha .... two days in fact :) , anyone tell me why I cant see the club I  am attached to in alpha? I was under the impression that it was still supposed to be here, yet I cant see it to get into it to talk to the club.

replies.body: It has been disabled until further notice. Check the dev team blogs whenever you can there is information that is worth reading.
